text: Krasny Klyuch () is a rural locality (a village) in Kameyevsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 3 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 21 km from Mishkino, 8 km from Kameyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Krasny Klyuch
